<task id="001" project="ai-spaarke-action-engine-r1">
  <metadata>
    <title>Architecture Spike — Runtime Topology &amp; Scheduler Choice</title>
    <phase>Phase 0: Architecture Spike</phase>
    <status>not-started</status>
    <estimated-hours>8</estimated-hours>
    <dependencies>none</dependencies>
    <blocks>010, 011, 012, 013, 014, 015, 016, 020, 021, 022, 023, 024, 025, 026, 030, 031, 032, 033, 034, 035, 036, 040, 041, 042, 043, 044, 045, 050, 051, 052, 053, 054, 055, 060, 061, 062, 063, 064, 065, 066, 070, 071, 072, 073, 090</blocks>
    <tags>bff-api, ai, architecture, spike, azure</tags>
    <rigor-hint>FULL</rigor-hint>
    <rigor-reason>Architecture decision with downstream blast radius across all Phase 1+ tasks; modifies plan.md and produces runtime ADR draft; tags include bff-api + ai</rigor-reason>
    <parallel-group>none</parallel-group>
    <parallel-safe>false</parallel-safe>
    <parallel-reason>Single critical-path task; blocks all subsequent work; main-session execution to preserve context for downstream task generation</parallel-reason>
